sequenceDiagram
    participant ESP32
    participant HiveMQ
    participant Backend

    ESP32->>HiveMQ: aquasense/network/zone/device/readings
    Backend->>HiveMQ: Subscribe aquasense/#
    HiveMQ-->>Backend: Sensor payload
    Backend->>Backend: Leak detection
    Backend->>HiveMQ: aquasense/network/zone/device/valve/command
    HiveMQ-->>ESP32: CLOSE / OPEN command
